  field_simp [abs_mul]
```

Now we can bound `|↑ℓ + 1 - ↑k|`. Since `ℓ ∈ range k`, we have `0 ≤ ℓ < k`, so `1 - k ≤ ℓ + 1 - k < 0`. Therefore, `|ℓ + 1 - k| < k`.

